                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/3864" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0944</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9539 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“靓女”出嫁：天津药物研究院的混改之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“Pretty Girl” Get Married： the Mixed Reform Road of  TIPR Pharmaceutical Responsible Co., Ltd</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">周建，邹美香，原东良，秦蓉，周飞谷，吴长军，杨威</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南开大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津药物研究院有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">20 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津药物研究院有限公司；招商局集团；混合所有制改革；2019百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">TIPR Pharmaceutical Responsible Co., Ltd, China Merchants Group, Mixed Ownership Reform</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">十八大以来，国有企业混合所有制改革进入试点和加速阶段。伴随着第三批混改试点工作的结束，混改的先行者积累了丰富的混改经验。本案例以具有地方特色医药国企的天津药物研究有限责任公司为研究对象，揭示药研院在提出混改想法之后，如何明确细化混改的具体方案并且选出最佳战略投资方，最终实现混改初步落地的改革历程。一方面，在混改方案的制定中，通过引进新的市场化机制，保证药研院的研发自主性；另一方面，在众多竞争的战略投资方当中，药研院充分考虑并选择了与其发展理念最为一致的招商局集团，最终从企业组织架构、企业文化、人力资源三个维度实现了混改的初步落地。本案例对于我国其他省份和医药行业的国有企业混改战略的设计和实施，实现国企混改的教学目的，具有显著的参考借鉴价值。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Since the 18th CPC National Congress, the mixed ownership reform of state-owned enterprises has entered a pilot and accelerated stage. With the end of the third batch of mixed reform pilot work, the forerunners of mixed reform have accumulated rich experience in mixed reform. This case takes TIPR Pharmaceutical Responsible Co., Ltd., a state-owned pharmaceutical company with local characteristics, as the research object, and reveals how the pharmaceutical research institute, after proposing the idea of mixed reform, clearly specifies the specific plan of mixed reform and selects the best strategic investor, finally realizing the initial landing of mixed reform. On the one hand, in the formulation of the mixed reform plan, through the introduction of a new market-oriented mechanism, to ensure the research and development autonomy of the drug research institute; On the other hand, among the numerous competitive strategic investors, the Institute fully considered and chose China Merchants Group, which is the most consistent with its development philosophy, and finally realized the initial landing of mixed reform from three dimensions of enterprise organizational structure, enterprise culture and human resources. This case has significant reference value for the design and implementation of the mixed reform strategy of state-owned enterprises in other provinces and the pharmaceutical industry in our country and for the realization of the teaching purpose of mixed reform of state-owned enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">混改战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019-09</td>
                            </tr>
